tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: I went for wisdom tooth pain which has made my lymh sollen. And after doctor analysis and xray , doctor pujari found it's in sleeping position and there is not much space for the extraction in x ray report they didn't able to find the root of the tooth how deep it was. First doctor pujari clean my tooth decay and filling. Then the extraction should be done by oral surgeon. He booked the appointment for next day. My anesthesia doctor was so clear about the details and symptoms. Then sugeon came and he made some analysis and during my surgery and after opening he found that tooth is stuck very deep down they have to break it using drilling he took pauses and was very patients with me. Comfort me multiple times. It took nearly 2 hours with proper extraction. At last I am so happy with the result and with doctor deepak conversations, humor, to keep me calm and complete the surgery. Clinic is small and conjusted but you didn't feel unattended doctors where really experienced. They only take decision after full analysis and give prescription accordingly. It's second day after my surgery and I am recovering smoothly. Really appreciated
Highly recommended to visit for any dental queries.Friendly approach and dr Deepak is giving accurate precautions
